             was indicted for <rs id="t17950520-17-off95" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17950520-17-off95" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17950520-17-off95" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17950520-17-cd96" type="crimeDate">21st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950520-17-off95 t17950520-17-cd96"></join>, two yards of printed cotton, value 5s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17950520-17-victim187" type="victimName">
                     Alexander 
                     Johnson
                  <interp inst="t17950520-17-victim187" type="surname" value="Johnson"></interp>
